data.description: Beautiful one story home with a two car garage, 3bed, 2bath boasting solar panels. March Electric bill $9.  With an open floor plan, vaulted ceilings, pretty upgraded kitchen with granite countertops. Primary bedroom has an open fireplace as does the living room. There are plenty of options for entertaining your family inside or outside on the cover deck.  Enjoy the beautiful mature trees and rose bushes. Conveniently located by major highways and shopping centers.
